The paper deals with information spread and diffusion cascades, which are topics related to social networks and graph theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also discusses algorithms and their performance, which suggests the sub-categories cs.SD (Software Engineering) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The formal proof presented in the paper indicates the sub-category cs.SY (Systems and Control), and the experimental results suggest the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning).
